name: Alex Flies a Plane - My First Solo Flight
description:
You might not have heard much from me over the last couple weeks, and that's because I've been hard at work on my Private Pilot License!

Just last week, I went for my first solo, and I wanted to share a bit of that! Enjoy this GoPro footage :)

With thanks to Downwind Aviation for the audio cable and for spotting me! Go check him out for more flying footage: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMaet5jCY4_JN2N0qsdRh7w
